{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "7e3bbe39-c7d6-4d89-b729-bd1b7bfd8eab", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7e3bbe39-c7d6-4d89-b729-bd1b7bfd8eab@1.pkg/1772597691719/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597692008", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7e3bbe39-c7d6-4d89-b729-bd1b7bfd8eab@1.pkg/1772597691719/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597692008"}, "identifier": "7e3bbe39-c7d6-4d89-b729-bd1b7bfd8eab", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查理解真正的友谊的价值。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>这句名言的意思是：与品德高尚的人相处，就像进入充满芝兰香气的屋子，久了便融入其中。强调朋友对人的正向塑造作用，核心主旨是志趣相投、品德相近，或是好的朋友起到的积极影响作用。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：形影不离与题目主旨不相符合，题目强调的是志趣相投。因此A错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：题目中的这句名言强调好的朋友对我们的正面影响，使我们自己与朋友之间实现道德与品行上的趋同与进步，因此志同道合正确，因此B正确。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：互相竞争与题目主旨无关，故C错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：真正的朋友应该在一定程度上彼此迁就，但&ldquo;彼此迁就&rdquo;与这句名言主旨无关。因此D错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选B</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）《孔子家语》中有一句名言：&ldquo;与善人居，如入芝兰之室，久而不闻其香，即与之化矣。&rdquo;这告诉我们真正的朋友应该（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）《孔子家语》中有一句名言：“与善人居，如入芝兰之室，久而不闻其香，即与之化矣。”这告诉我们真正的朋友应该（    ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7e3bbe39-c7d6-4d89-b729-bd1b7bfd8eab@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977936250", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>形影不离 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>志同道合 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>互相竞争 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>彼此迁就</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）《孔子家语》中有一句名言：&ldquo;与善人居，如入芝兰之室，久而不闻其香，即与之化矣。&rdquo;这告诉我们真正的朋友应该（ &nbsp; &nbsp;）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-